Christian Abercrombie has undergone emergency surgery after suffering a head injury
Tennessee State Tigers linebacker Christian Abercrombie underwent emergency surgery after suffering a head injury during Saturday’s game when his team lost to Vanderbilt Commodores 31-27, Tennessee’s Mike Organ said.
